               cco2:ont00001760 <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/okea/OntologyOfKnowledgeEngineeringArtifacts> .


###  https://github.com/jonathanvajda/okea/ont000090
okea:ont000090 rdf:type owl:Class ;
               rdfs:subClassOf cceo:ApplicationSoftware ;
               rdfs:label "Graph Visualizer"@en ;
