               cco2:ont00001760 <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/okea/OntologyOfKnowledgeEngineeringArtifacts> .


###  https://github.com/jonathanvajda/okea/ont000091
okea:ont000091 rdf:type owl:Class ;
               rdfs:subClassOf okea:ont000030 ;
               rdfs:label "Graph Database Configuration"@en ;
               skos:altLabel "DB Config Asset"@en ;
