               skos:example "A `config.ttl` file initializing an Apache Jena TDB2 database instance"@en ;
               skos:scopeNote "A deployment configuration asset setting up cache parameters, rule sets, and access tokens for a graph engine."@en ;
               cco2:ont00001760 <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/okea/OntologyOfKnowledgeEngineeringArtifacts> .


###  https://github.com/jonathanvajda/okea/ont000092
