               skos:example "A UML diagram mapping out corporate business relationships"@en ;
               skos:scopeNote "An abstract, high-level structural map visualizing business domains prior to coding formal logic rules."@en ;
               cco2:ont00001760 <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/okea/OntologyOfKnowledgeEngineeringArtifacts> .


