               skos:altLabel "Formal Ontological Model"@en ;
               skos:definition "An Information Content Entity that represents domain entities, relations, and constraints in a technology-independent formal structure designed to guide implementation or reasoning."@en ;
               skos:example "An un-serialized representation of classes and exact property constraints"@en ;
               skos:scopeNote "A rigorous, technology-agnostic representation mapping domain classes and precise logical restrictions."@en ;
               cco2:ont00001760 <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/okea/OntologyOfKnowledgeEngineeringArtifacts> .


