               skos:example "A production-ready `.ttl` file deployed to an enterprise server"@en ;
               skos:scopeNote "The actual, physical serialized data files uploaded into production database engines."@en ;
               cco2:ont00001760 <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/okea/OntologyOfKnowledgeEngineeringArtifacts> .


