               skos:example "A file containing explicit equivalence relationships between two distinct schemas"@en ;
               skos:scopeNote "A formal file asset declaring structural cross-model equivalencies to allow data to traverse different systems."@en ;
               cco2:ont00001760 <https://github.com/jonathanvajda/okea/OntologyOfKnowledgeEngineeringArtifacts> .


